QuestData.Title: Valley of the Four Winds
QuestData.Description: Yarr, the Jade Forest be goin through some violent reconstruction, but the Valley of the Four Winds is ripe for explorin. I can help ye on yer way if ye wants to explore it. Be sure to check out me wares for some equipment that may help ye on yer journey.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak to Private Tim P. O'Rary in the Valley of the Four Winds.

Objectives.Objective: Speak with Private Tim P. O'Rary in Valley of the Four Winds
